US MASTERS RESIDENTIAL PROPERTY (USA) FUND, Petitioner,
v.
NEW JERSEY DEPARTMENT OF ENVIRONMENTAL PROTECTION-FINANCIAL SERVICES ELEMENT, Respondent. C-1031 September Term 2017
081137 Supreme Court of New Jersey. August 1, 2018

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-003632-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is granted.
